
'''= advocate of Democratic Internet TV and co-developer of [[Miro]]'''

=Bio=

"Dean Jansen is part of the Special Projects team at the Participatory Culture Foundation. The PCF is the non-profit organization which creates the Democracy Internet TV Platform, soon to be named Miro.

DemocracyPlayer aims to change the way mass-media works, by giving control of Internet TV back to the public. You can control how you download, re-mix, and distribute different video channels. In essence DemocracyPlayer lowers the bar for anyone to create their own online TV channel." (http://kruufm.com/33-open-views-dean-jansen-participatory-culture-foundation) 

